title: Garbanzo Mediterranean Grill - Boulder
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Mediterranean, Middle Eastern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Casual, quick service chain restaurant with locations in Colorado. Offers a variety of traditional Mediterranean dishes customizable to special dietary needs. Build your meal by walking the line with an employee selecting ingredients. Each item is clearly labeled with the name as well as the dietary needs it meets including vegetarian, vegan, and gluten free.
